{"tid":1421273,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"良心企業JYP 「TWICE師姐」遭浪費7年！暴怒嗆：我要唱歌 鐵心離開JYP","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:18:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6336beeaa08ff9985143a32aa19f887ee8bd3f","tid":1421273,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"南韓女星朴智敏2011年演唱一首《Rolling In The Deep》一戰成名，她當年年僅15歲，因身材圓潤嗓音宏亮被封為「韓版小愛黛兒」，連CNN都爭相報導。她拿下冠軍後，2012年簽進JYP娛樂，身為TWICE師姐的她卻幾乎沒什麼音樂作品，好聲音遭埋沒，曾在節目上爆氣狂罵，直到近日合約到期，她鐵心離開待了7年的JYP，團體15&amp;名存實亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4286/d4286541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4286%2Fd4286541.jpg&h=325a6283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴智敏2011年演唱一首《Rolling In The Deep》一戰成名。（圖／翻攝自SBS）<br />\n<br />\n朴智敏簽給JYP娛樂後，隔年與同齡白藝潾組成15&amp;，團體只出了一張正規專輯《Sugar》，便幾乎消失在樂壇，她則是成了節目《After School Club》主持人，偶爾唱唱戲劇OST，音樂才能完全被埋沒，導致心裡積了許多怨念，曾在節目上抱怨「JYP，我是一名歌手，我要唱歌！」這段看似充滿節目效果的開玩笑言論，實則引起很多討論，不少人為她抱屈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4286/d4286539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4286%2Fd4286539.jpg&h=85de14ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴智敏當年在節目上爆紅，簽給JYP卻沒什麼代表作。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n如今7年合約到期，JYP於6日宣佈與朴智敏討論過後，雙方確定不續簽約，祝福朴智敏未來會有新的開始，而她所隸屬得的團體15&amp;名存實亡，同齡成員白藝潾至今也仍在考慮要不要繼續簽約，結果還未公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJYP真係好好人 比佢唱OST 又比佢做主持<br />\n點解JYP對佢咁好都要上節目埋怨<br />\n咁都要走 真係好25<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正一25女"},{"pid":"4f17eccd674847be8e6320642c539399bb990bf9","tid":1421273,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"講真我覺得JYP好過YG好多啦<br />\n比咁多JOB佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dcf0e122d783279c9c21fffc3be7ea62aa039a","tid":1421273,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"冇JYP FAMILY一齊入黎屌25女??"},{"pid":"680a1d8900d1aebf0d1908fbf5be5fc17a3d24f3","tid":1421273,"uid":294121,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"我地jyp有twice寶就夠了<br />\n其他垃圾好行唔送"},{"pid":"661ee0d6bb4ea674652f2e2b9c62832e95a2a324","tid":1421273,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2338b6b0d36248b40cb280a1f1033b13aee2bc4","tid":1421273,"uid":2781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"jyp有twice就夠其他洗乜care<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed63131ab151fb9fb0d9fb1e08733e21d94d4e1d","tid":1421273,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99e6e90121e9536ad94233818f4c4f865079c58","tid":1421273,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"去YG啦"},{"pid":"8a43d78832a18a2e260c71ea53a2e8a9debaa829","tid":1421273,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2338b6b0d36248b40cb280a1f1033b13aee2bc4","tid":1421273,"uid":2781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"jyp有twice就夠其他洗乜care<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"連秀智都可以唔要"},{"pid":"31f6416981ae08fe42e39a2d5b2664603c5ac8cf","tid":1421273,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a43d78832a18a2e260c71ea53a2e8a9debaa829","tid":1421273,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2338b6b0d36248b40cb280a1f1033b13aee2bc4","tid":1421273,"uid":2781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"jyp有twice就夠其他洗乜care<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:16:38.000Z","msg