9d9b15108198dcec8029dff3f46b843f42bc8","tid":1421273,"uid":89660,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"7 years with JYP  I was more than happy to be one of the singers with all the amazing peoples. I&rsquo;m sure going to miss all of this but it&rsquo;s also a start for me. Thank you for supporting me through out the years. Promise you I will never forget the warm loves #ThankyouJYP 🙏🏻<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jiminpark07/status/1158636172345655296?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjiminpark07%2Fstatus%2F1158636172345655296%3Fs%3D21&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCpggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=4c99bf3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjiminpark07%2Fstatus%2F1158636172345655296%3Fs%3D21&h=cc68131e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jiminpark07/status/1158636172345655296?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好來好去"},{"pid":"82b4dee950cf5a4f55f0f2766a344721f1226823","tid":1421273,"uid":138658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"仲有白藝潾同白娥娟都被JYP害鳩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c621edafe9679fdf8d40808ba8ee177e788db6","tid":1421273,"uid":119771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"講真 佢係有實力既 啲歌係幾好聽<br />\n但咁多年都紅唔起就知咩事啦...真係冇咩觀眾緣<br />\n仲貼錢幫佢出碟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}